column2: select top # dbo.fSpecidFromSDSS (q.plate, q.mjd, q.fiberid, #) as specObjID, q.ra, q.dec, sp.psfMag_u as u, sp.psfMag_g as g, sp.psfMag_r as r, sp.psfMag_i as i, sp.psfMag_z as z, sp.psfMagErr_u as err_u, sp.psfMagErr_g as err_g, sp.psfMagErr_r as err_r, sp.psfMagErr_i as err_i, sp.psfMagErr_z as err_z, sp.z as redshihft, sp.zErr as redshift_error from mydb.dr1#q as q, SpecPhoto as sp into mydb.dr1#q_photometry_boss where q.spectro = # and sp.plate = q.plate and sp.mjd = q.mjd and sp.fiberid = q.fiberid
